data.description: Implemented integrated API solutions using Node.js within an AWS Lambda framework for a Digital Bank service project. Utilized DynamoDB and RedshiftData as primary data storage solutions. Collaborated with an Agile Scrum team, leveraging Atlassian tools for project management and coordination
Developed and maintained Serverless architecture using NodeJS and AWS services in a Translation Service project (www.locale.to)
Created sports betting web services and APIs, alongside developing reel games for slot betting systems. Employed technologies including ReactJS, VueJS, and NodeJS for implementation.
Primarily accountable for creating, scaling, and sustaining a comprehensive real-time online casino web service. Utilized NodeJS for backend development and Laravel for frontend development.

Specialized in Node.js and AngularJS development to create an online school system initially hosted at pd360.com, now accessible at app.frontlineeducation.com. The system remains in use by schools across the United States to the present day.
